title: Jessica Lange wins an Emmy Award for American Horror Story 2012
author: Stanley Ipkiss
comment: As others have said, it's funny that 4 of those nominees appeared on AHS. They really do know how to cast em
What the hell is with the audience? A lot of them not clapping or anything. Show some respect. Jessica Lange is one of the most talented actresses today.
4 of the nominees appeared in AHS
When Jessica Lange's name is called and wins an award you STAND and applaud her. She's an amazing actress and has won 2 Oscars, a Tony, Emmys, Golden Globes. I don't care if it's the Emmys or not.
She totally deserved this! She's always my favourite in AHS! ×
